# Text Snippets (`touch-text-snippets`)

## When to Use
- Store reusable text for emails, support replies, and templates.

## Trigger
- Feature ID: `text-snippets.search`
- Commands: `text / snippet`

## Core Capabilities
- Text snippets library: phrases and common templates.
- Supported platforms: `win32, darwin, linux`

## Config & Data
- Config/data files: `snippets.json`
- Plugin directory: `plugins/touch-text-snippets`

## Permissions
- Required: `clipboard.write`; Optional: `clipboard.read`

## Quick Start
1. In CoreBox, type `text`.
2. Press Enter on the action you need.
3. Grant permissions when prompted.
